🎼We are learning the ukulele from @yousician (not a sponsored post 🤣).
.

I actually bought this ukulele years ago but gave up trying to learn because pressing on the strings hurt my fingers...and I don’t want to have calluses, yes I’m so weak!! Any tips? Can I wear gloves or something? 🧤😬?
.
But look! My son is learning and he’s doing better than me. Super proud!.
.
.
#sgmummy #sgkids #sgmusic #yousician #ukulelesg #stayhomesg #sgunited #7maycb #nobbtstill06may
